Question: In each image, at least one pelican perches on some kind of platform in front of the same double-peaked building in the background.

Reference Answer: False

Original program:

```
ANSWER0=VQA(image=LEFT,question='Is there at least one pelican perching on some kind of platform in front of the same double-peaked building in the background?')
ANSWER1=VQA(image=RIGHT,question='Is there at least one pelican perching on some kind of platform in front of the same double-peaked building in the background?')
ANSWER2=EVAL(expr='{ANSWER0} and {ANSWER1}')
FINAL_ANSWER=RESULT(var=ANSWER2)
```
